      {
        "id": 3961,
        "name": "Feng Qu",
        "username": "fengqu",
        "avatar_template": "https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/f/85f322/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-04-17T23:59:27.882Z",
        "cooked": "<p>We have 3 data centers(they can be configured in one region or two regions or 3 regions) and we want to achieve HA, high throughput and low latency.<br>\n\u2022\tIs there a way to make all 3 data center local read/write?<br>\no\tIf not, can we make 2 data center to provide local read/write?<br>\n\uf0a7\tIf so, what\u2019s usage for 3rd data center, can we read from it?<br>\n\uf0a7\tIf not, can we make it one data center local read/write and other two data center read?</p>\n<p>Appreciate your feedback.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 4,
        "updated_at": "2019-04-17T23:59:40.632Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
